Gadgetbahn is term used by [http://www.publictransit.us/PublicTransitUS.php?catid=20&blogid=8 transit professionals] to describe infeasible transportation concepts. Gadgetbahn has a long and controversial [http://www.lib.berkeley.edu/news_events/exhibits/futuristics/index.html history]

Perhaps the most well-known transportation concept to be labled gadgetbahn is [[Personal Rapid Transit]] or PRT.

